263
00:16:01,030 --> 00:16:02,320
If you can't explain it to us,

264
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,510
just explain it to him.

265
00:16:03,510 --> 00:16:04,030
Yes.

266
00:16:04,190 --> 00:16:05,390
If you don't explain,

267
00:16:05,430 --> 00:16:06,630
