782
00:39:34,670 --> 00:39:36,730
Your Grace, please think it through.

783
00:39:39,030 --> 00:39:39,700
Doctor,

784
00:39:41,070 --> 00:39:42,070
please

785
00:39:42,440 --> 00:39:43,770
keep this confidential

786
00:39:43,880 --> 00:39:45,450
